data.description: NEW PRICE--Motivated Seller! Great Location! No City Taxes! No HOA! Opportunity to own a home with almost an acre lot in Wake County. (1/2 acre lot behind home included in sale--4231 Hilltop Needmore Rd) 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, Hardwood floors, Tankless Water heater, fridge, w/d, newer heater and window ac unit, and 2 sheds convey. Step outside onto your large deck, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relax among the natural surroundings. Close proximity to Hilltop Needmore Park with walking trails, soon to be new Community Center and Elementary School. Minutes from the new 540 Expressway opening late spring.
